OL,3,CHorse Racing cancelled across UK but
OL,4,Chistoric Carlisle meeting to go ahead
OL,6,FThe decision to call off various horse
OL,7,Frace meetings across the UK has been
OL,8,Fbranded "very sensible" although the
OL,9,Fhistoric Carlisle Bell and Plate is
OL,10,Fset to go ahead on Wednesday.
OL,12,FAs temperatures soar and a red weather
OL,13,Fwarning comes into effect across
OL,14,Fsouthern England a decision was made
OL,15,Fby the British Horseracing Authority
OL,16,F(BHA) to reschedule meetings planned
OL,17,Ffor Wednesday.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
