OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1782404310
OL,3,CHorse Racing cancelled across UK but
OL,4,Chistoric Carlisle meeting to go ahead
OL,6,FOn Monday morning fixtures at
OL,7,FWorcester, Salisbury, Kempton and Ffos
OL,8,FLas were called off in the interests
OL,9,Fof safety for the horses and
OL,10,Fparticipants.
OL,12,FThe BHA also announced that fixtures
OL,13,Fat Newmarket and Nottingham on
OL,14,FThursday have been brought forward so
OL,15,Fthey are finished before the hottest
OL,16,Fpart of the day while the two-mile
OL,17,FDereham Handicap at Newmarket will now
OL,18,Ftake place there on Friday.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1782404310
OL,3,CHorse Racing cancelled across UK but
OL,4,Chistoric Carlisle meeting to go ahead
OL,6,FThe BHA's hot weather policy states
OL,7,Fthat where racecourses fall within a
OL,8,Fred warning zone, the fixture will be
OL,9,Fabandoned. Horses also must not be
OL,10,Ftravelled from or through areas that
OL,11,Fhave red warnings in place.
OL,13,FCarlisle's meeting in Cumbria is still
OL,14,Fscheduled to take place on Wednesday,
OL,15,Ffeaturing the historic Carlisle Bell
OL,16,Fand Cumberland Plate.
OL,18,FThe Carlisle Bell is the world's
OL,19,Foldest sporting trophy, having been
OL,20,Ffirst contested in 1599.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
