OL,3,CHorse Racing cancelled across UK but
OL,4,Chistoric Carlisle meeting to go ahead
OL,6,FIn a statement Carlisle Racecourse
OL,7,Fsaid: "This historic race is the
OL,8,Fcentrepiece of a thrilling day that's
OL,9,Ffirmly rooted in tradition yet
OL,10,Fbursting with excitement.
OL,12,F"Run alongside the fiercely
OL,13,Fcompetitive Cumberland Plate and the
OL,14,Fprestigious listed Eternal Stakes,
OL,15,Fit's a day that captures the spirit of
OL,16,Fracing at its very best."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
