CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1782404310
OL,3,CHorse Racing cancelled across UK but
OL,4,Chistoric Carlisle meeting to go ahead
OL,6,FTrainer Alex Hales, who had been due
OL,7,Fto have two runners at Worcester on
OL,8,FWednesday, supported the decision to
OL,9,Fcall off the meeting insisting horse
OL,10,Fwelfare comes first.
OL,12,F"We just have to be sensible. We try
OL,13,Fto work the horses earlier and get the
OL,14,Fmain bits of work done before the sun
OL,15,Freally comes up and, with travelling,
OL,16,Fthe lorries have fans in them now to
OL,17,Fkeep the temperatures down," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
