CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1782404310
OL,3,CHorse Racing cancelled across UK but
OL,4,Chistoric Carlisle meeting to go ahead
OL,6,F"But if the temperatures are getting
OL,7,Fas high as predicted keeping the
OL,8,Fhorses hydrated with plenty of
OL,9,Felectrolytes as well is very important.
OL,11,F"We are constantly monitoring the
OL,12,Fhorses and if they are showing signs
OL,13,Fof getting too hot we would pull them
OL,14,Fout and get them under the hosepipe
OL,15,Fand cool them off that way.
OL,17,F"But I think the BHA have been very
OL,18,Fsensible and the whole industry is
OL,19,Fsensible with it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU{D@RO]
